{"type":"message","id":"e85036db","parentId":"76108d00","timestamp":"2026-04-02T20:17:26.636Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Hecho. Ya quedó corregido a:\n\n- **lunes a viernes**\n- **8:00 AM a 8:00 PM**\n- **cada 2 horas**\n- **America/Bogota**\n\nSe lo actualicé a:\n- **Ares**\n- **Hestia**\n- **Prometeo**\n\nCron ahora:\n- `0 8-20/2 * * 1-5`\n\nO sea disparos en:\n- 8:00\n- 10:00\n- 12:00\n- 2:00 PM\n- 4:00 PM\n- 6:00 PM\n- 8:00 PM\n\nSi quieres, también les puedo poner una regla adicional para que el de **8:00 PM** sea más tipo **cierre corto del día** que simple seguimiento.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e047052a68bd2a20169ceced4cc648191864bbf3821ecb75c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":427,"output":180,"cacheRead":102400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103007,"cost":{"input":0.0010675,"output":0.0027,"cacheRead":0.025599999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.029367499999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775161037117,"responseId":"resp_0e047052a68bd2a20169ceced0f428819188f8f96702399a85"}}
